 <title xml:id="SysServices">Disable Autofs Daemon</title>
 <para>
  Disables the autofs daemon. The autofs daemon facilitates automated
  mounting of filesystems.
  <indexterm>
   <primary>autofs</primary>
  </indexterm>
 </para>
